Tswalo: This award winning offering gives a platform to the art of solo performances and how they are carried by movement and voice. It takes the audience through the contradictory nature of existing by highlighting the relationship between chaos and beauty, blood and birth as well as love and war. Details: The production takes places until October 27 at The Market Theatre, 56 Margaret Mcingana Street, Newtown.
